Package: diaQTLSimulate
Type: Package
Title: Simulate multi-population for linkage analysis in autopolyploids and QTL
Version: 0.2
Author: Rodrigo R Amadeu and Chaozhi Zheng
Maintainer: Rodrigo R Amadeu <rramadeu@ufl.edu>
Description: Simulate multi-population for linkage analysis in autopolyploids and creates the input files for PolyOrigin software. Simulates QTL in top of the simulated genotypes and creates input files for diaQTL software. It also contains a internal wrap-up of `diaQTL::scan1` function to do the genome scanning internally.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Imports: stringr (>= 1.4.0),
          updog,
          parallel,
          foreach,
          diaQTL,
          doParallel
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
